profile:
The GMRS Woodworking is a Canadian company that provides carpentry and woodworking services throughout the Montreal area. We are expert in kitchen stripping, kitchen renovation, custom kitchen fabrication, kitchen resurfacing and kitchens / bathrooms installation. We have been developping techniques to achieve exceptional finish work at exceptional prices . Our team is made of skilled professionals with many years of experience in the field. We offer you our expertise, our sense of perfectionism, our creativity and our love for wood.
The aim is to offer a quality service and flawless finish that exceeds your expectations at affordable prices. Also, we are able to bring a modern touch to your kitchen while keeping their authenticity.

After an estimate of the proposed work, our team will map out your ideas and the changes needed to restore your home beauty. A personalized planification of the project will be proposed based on your own needs, your lifestyle, your taste and your budget.
Our team works on all woodworking projects to improve the functionality of your kitchen, redevelopment or expansion of your bathroom. We also do planning for interior spaces.

The renovation of your kitchen or your bathroom will increase the value of your home, freshen its appearance, make it more cozy and functional.

Cabinetmakers involved throughout the Greater Montreal area.

Want to refresh the look of your home? Restore the youthful look to your kitchen? Do you want to simply do a new remodeling project? Do not hesitate to contact Ébénisterie GMRS for your project. Our team assures monitoring and personalized service from the design plans to the end of your renovation project .
